Shipping Tropical Fish from Rockland Aquarium

All of our door-to-door orders are sent using Next Day Air. We ship two days a week. Monday and Tuesday or Tuesday and Wednesday if Monday is a Holiday. Most orders received will be shipped the following week.

Please text or call us for pick up. 845-269-1530.

Rockland Aquarium

132 Route 304

Bardonia, NY 10954

Be mindful of the laws in your state before placing your order! If the fish selected are illegal in the state you reside in, your order will be cancelled.

Where do we ship from?

We ship from our location located in Bardonia, New York:

Shipping rates:

We are happy to offer a shipping discount that saves you a considerable amount compared to retail prices. Check our Flat Rate shipping at check out or do FREE store pick up..

We do not ship to Puerto Rico, Hawaii, and Alaska.
